sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant GameController
    participant InputHandler
    participant PauseMenu as Pause Menu UI
    participant SnakeHead
    participant SnakeTail
    participant Apple
    participant Grid as Grid/TileMap

    Note over GameController: Game is paused<br>No movement, no updates

    GameController -> PauseMenu: displayPauseMenu()

    loop waiting for unpause
        GameController -> InputHandler: checkForInput()
        InputHandler --> GameController: userChoice
    end

    alt user selects "Resume"
        GameController -> GameController: changeState(RUNNING)
        Note over GameController: Gameplay resumes
    else other menu option
        GameController -> PauseMenu: showOptionScreen()
    end